From 8ad998fe826a0537a3c44b4560002865d74f035c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Joseph Magly <1159087+jmagly@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 04:46:34 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 22/26] fix(m135): remove stale :blink target dep from blink
 platform BUILD.gn

Patch 0012 replaced the :carbonyl dep with :blink in
third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn, introducing a
carbonyl::blink API. Patch 0013 reverted that API back to
carbonyl::Bridge without removing the :blink dep from BUILD.gn.
The :blink GN target was never defined, causing gn gen to fail with
"unresolved dependency: needs //carbonyl/src/browser:blink".

Remove the stale dep. Platform uses carbonyl::Bridge from :bridge.
---
 third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn b/third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn
index 213456454c7d5..79c581e819e8f 100644
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/platform/BUILD.gn
@@ -1803,7 +1803,6 @@ component("platform") {
     "//base:base_static",
     "//base/allocator:buildflags",
     "//build:chromecast_buildflags",
-    "//carbonyl/src/browser:blink",
     "//carbonyl/src/browser:bridge",
     "//cc",
     "//cc/ipc",
